  <trk>
    <name>Vineyard terrace hike in Martigny</name>
    <desc>A circular hike through the vineyard terraces above Martigny, passing by the medieval castle and the wine village Plan Cerisier. Enjoy the breathtaking view of Martigny and the Rhone Valley.</desc>
